[div class=p 
	"Actually, my first submission for this game was a little over 19 years ago. I hope that I can submit another improvement on 26 May 2024 to do a proper "20 years ago today" meme.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Maniac Mansion, an iconic 1990 NES game, invites players into a mysterious and humorously bizarre adventure. Set in a creepy mansion, players must choose and control a team of characters, each with unique skills and personalities, to rescue a kidnapped cheerleader from an evil scientist and his twisted family. With its innovative point-and-click gameplay, clever puzzles, and multiple endings, Maniac Mansion offers great freedom and replayability.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"My earliest submission on 26 May 2004 clocked in at 9:51.93. I found a lot of glitches between that submission and my last MM submission on 29 Jan 2008, knocking the time down to 6:29.77. Then for a long time, nothing happened. But recently, the Maniac Mansion speedrunning community found four new major glitches that save a lot of time. Thus I had to make a new movie and beat all known records.
	$LF
]div
